OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOften large amounts of cloud
OL,6,Fwith some brightness. Drizzle and some
OL,7,Fmorning rain affecting coastal areas.
OL,8,FChance of showers in western areas
OL,9,Flater in the day. Feeling warm by
OL,10,Fafternoon, with light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FEvening showers, mainly
OL,13,Faffecting northern and western parts
OL,14,Ffading then a dry night with some
OL,15,Fcloud breaks and light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
