OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FWednesday generally dry and
OL,6,Fincreasingly bright, with sunny spells
OL,7,Flikely across the region. Light winds
OL,8,Ffreshening a little in afternoon.
OL,9,FPatchy rain arriving later in the
OL,10,Fnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FCloud
OL,13,Fand showery rain during Thursday
OL,14,Fclearing by early afternoon, then
OL,15,Fbright, Friday and Saturday probably
OL,16,Fmostly dry and breezy, with clear or
OL,17,Fsunny spells. Temperatures mostly
OL,18,Fabove average throughout.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
